This code book contains the details how the final tidy data was retrived using the various file downloaded.

Below are steps

 1. Downloaded the zip file from https://d396qusza40orc.cloudfront.net/getdata%2Fprojectfiles%2FUCI%20HAR%20Dataset.zip 
 2. Added the files into the working directory
 3. Loaded the metadata (or standing data) into data frame.
 4. Loaded the data from test and train files into different data frames.
 5. Merged train and test datafarames together
 6. Named the attributes appropriately.
 7. Combined the different parts of the data together to give meaning to it.
 
Below are the list of variables retrived in the result set.
More details of them can be found here... "UCI HAR Dataset\features_info.txt"

